g src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我諗會學ps<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n完全唔識畫圖同唔係做個類嘅design<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nBtw有啲三合一嘅課程抵唔抵報 以你過來人嘅身份<br />\n(Ps, Ai , indesign)"},{"pid":"8514dfa2e45f5a3a0328a379e9186f6f58ee033a","tid":147723,"uid":5716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T08:27:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔建議報濕鳩課程，有心既上youtube睇教程再自己摸索下。"},{"pid":"1fc2811ee72ed784094d2f4df17c776e64be8214","tid":147723,"uid":9115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T12:14:07.000Z","msg":"濕鳩課程真係純粹教你每樣tools點用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但係真係學野上youtube好過"},{"pid":"5514448b108c7171caaa947420087a48c70d1726","tid":147723,"uid":26266,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T12:18:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>睇你想做咩design類型既工<br />\n<br />\n執相加filter、人像、去背景、普通加少少字個d就photoshop<br />\n真係晝圖晝公仔就AI<br />\n<br />\n我自己覺得photoshop易學d<br />\n以前細個CS2個年代我都係自學<br />\n家下大個覺得AI大自由度d可以變化多d<br />\n不過都仲係2樣一齊用緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我諗會學ps<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n完全唔識畫圖同唔係做個類嘅design<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nBtw有啲三合一嘅課程抵唔抵報 以你過來人嘅身份<br />\n(Ps, Ai , indesign)</blockquote><br />\nAi 繪圖<br />\nPs 執相、改圖<br />\nId 排版<br />\n<br />\n業餘玩玩下自學ps就夠"},{"pid":"e6261ffc7d3e029db03e4999aba3dad002159a49","tid":147723,"uid":5322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T12:43:55.000Z","msg":"講下係目的係乜，或者有無例子想做乜。 咁會易啲俾到建議你。"},{"pid":"b7397002c6034c943029d5504fb332d589bca351","tid":147723,"uid":77141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T12:48:13.000Z","msg":"如果整poster /卡片邊樣好？"},{"pid":"eb89677690944bd7e437b3da7d8e6384b8586ad7","tid":147723,"uid":56935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T12:51:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>如果整poster /卡片邊樣好？</blockquote><br />\n睇你想用咩風格<br />\n不過多數係兩樣一齊用架啦"},{"pid":"ef08a13c133d26c72751e47cdd95832fc7d6936f","tid":147723,"uid":61077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T12:52:06.000Z","msg":"ai 是p不到圖的"},{"pid":"5e206a8de80cbaf8d297cde09dfcef554bcb2456","tid":147723,"uid":48261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T12:56:13.000Z","msg":"有冇關於呢D 交流學下野 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb9b5fea32edfd7bfa0b74318200e82c5e8d7d9b","tid":147723,"uid":44346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T13:59:10.000Z","msg":"之前報左CU果個基礎電腦設計學用PS &amp; AI，廢到爆，阿sir淨係會叫你照notes做<br />\n<br />\n都係學其他巴打話齋，YouTube學啦<br />\n利申：自學左好多年（都係初學咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ），想要張Cert先報course<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"470303b0ce756cf3fdb7e5af7d886af8cb6fcd09","tid":147723,"uid":87650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T14:09:37.000Z","msg":"睇你學黎做咩，主要做普通平面設計ps同ai都係基本，最好識埋Indesign會方便d<br />\n如果想出去報course學唔洗諗住讀完course就做到, 可以學d基本設計概念, 印刷同網上分別, 然後慢慢自己摸下d 技術, 或youtube學技巧<br />\n<br />\n利申: wet9 designer, 想搵大錢唔好入行<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa06a5164e73a3937704a75e5b0c9eeec13044cc","tid":147723,"uid":77141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T14:14:45.000Z","msg":"初哥咩都唔識<br />\nPs唔知邊到學起好<br />\n有冇youtuber推介？"},{"pid":"c134c8c88dc7ad228557389ac0936e44e2f25338","tid":147723,"uid":80533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T14:33:14.000Z","msg":"非design專業人士建議：<br />\n<br />\n如果想自學Ps，請先download一大堆brush同pattern<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.brusheezy.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.brusheezy.com&d=bx%2Fd%2Fc%2BwyKmxZhRK7gjal6WGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=ff44ca4d\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.brusheezy.com</a><br />\n仲有Ps記得裝英文版<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之前有個同學裝19 pirate copy中文版<br />\nd譯名又難聽d位置又唔同<br />\n仲要我教我真係想講粗口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4bb628982e349305944711b32554d021a8a94df6","tid":147723,"uid":87650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T14:35:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>初哥咩都唔識<br />\nPs唔知邊到學起好<br />\n有冇youtuber推介？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實我覺得初學可以學左三原色關係, 同layer既概念, 但呢d 睇片未必理解到, 因為通常睇片都係step by step 學想做到既effect,<br />\n<a href=\"https://helpx.adobe.com/photoshop/using/layer-basics.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhelpx.adobe.com%2Fphotoshop%2Fusing%2Flayer-basics.html&d=bx%2Fd%2Fc%2BwyKmxZhRK7gjal6WGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=abc3af1c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://helpx.adobe.com/photoshop/using/layer-basics.html</a><br />\n呢條link有講layer既概念, 三原色關係巴打有興趣可以慢慢解釋你聽<br />\n<br />\n了解左呢2樣野之後可以慢慢遂個effect上youtube search黎學, 我自己覺得鬼佬果d 片易明d...<br />\n<br />\n唔知其他高手有無其他見解"},{"pid":"76247fda0f2f5455382fb81025cc1023f1fbbd86","tid":147723,"uid":34647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T05:38:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>睇你學黎做咩，主要做普通平面設計ps同ai都係基本，最好識埋Indesign會方便d<br />\n如果想出去報course學唔洗諗住讀完course就做到, 可以學d基本設計概念, 印刷同網上分別, 然後慢慢自己摸下d 技術, 或youtube學技巧<br />\n<br />\n利申: wet9 designer, 想搵大錢唔好入行<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n諗住遲下去啲studio room/廣告雜誌到做<br />\n見佢好多都要精通ps&amp; ai, 一係就話識is a plus咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75aff8674517a4bd5da9479fe70963d677e1f0e0","tid":147723,"uid":34647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T05:39:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>初哥咩都唔識<br />\nPs唔知邊到學起好<br />\n有冇youtuber推介？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實我覺得初學可以學左三原色關係, 同layer既概念, 但呢d 睇片未必理解到, 因為通常睇片都係step by step 學想做到既effect,<br />\n<a href=\"https://helpx.adobe.com/photoshop/using/layer-basics.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhelpx.adobe.com%2Fphotoshop%2Fusing%2Flayer-basics.html&d=bx%2Fd%2Fc%2BwyKmxZhRK7gjal6WGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=abc3af1c\" target=\"_blank\">https://helpx.adobe.com/photoshop/using/layer-basics.html</a><br />\n呢條link有講layer既概念, 三原色關係巴打有興趣可以慢慢解釋你聽<br />\n<br />\n了解左呢2樣野之後可以慢慢遂個effect上youtube search黎學, 我自己覺得鬼佬果d 片易明d...<br />\n<br />\n唔知其他高手有無其他見解</blockquote><br />\n上網睇鬼佬教真係幾有用 幾簡單易明 <br />\nBtw以前有玩過下p相咁 所以基本野都明明地<br />\n我覺得玩/用得多就ok"},{"pid":"4e0f6377ee4b2aea2d37188c5b5f788dde21b80a","tid":147723,"uid":87650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T18:31:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>睇你學黎做咩，主要做普通平面設計ps同ai都係基本，最好識埋Indesign會方便d<br />\n如果想出去報course學唔洗諗住讀完course就做到, 可以學d基本設計概念, 印刷同網上分別, 然後慢慢自己摸下d 技術, 或youtube學技巧<br />\n<br />\n利申: wet9 designer, 想搵大錢唔好入行<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n諗住遲下去啲studio room/廣告雜誌到做<br />\n見佢好多都要精通ps&amp; ai, 一係就話識is a plus咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n如果係影相既studio room, 多數就係ps 同lightroom行先<br />\n廣告雜誌就多數要3個software都識, 或者入左去先慢慢學, 但岩岩起步會好辛苦, 加油巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}